      <title>德克萨斯玻璃回收商因利率上涨而申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/texan-glass-recycler-files-for-bankruptcy-hit-by-rising-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[再生玻璃供应商战略材料公司(Strategic Materials Inc.)因受到利率上升和竞争加剧的挤压而申请破产。]]></description>
