      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:43:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔出售给巴克莱银行战略审查带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/barclays-shares-fall-after-qatar-s-wealth-fund-reveals-stake-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔财富基金出售了近一半的股份后，巴克莱银行股价下跌了 4.5%，这一出人意料的举动增加了该银行向投资者发布战略前几个月首席执行官 C.S. Venkatakrishnan 的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/barclays-shares-fall-after-qatar-s-wealth-fund-reveals-stake-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 08:28:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
